## Show All Technology Data

### Endpoint  
**`POST /site/technology`**

### Request Query Parameters  

| Parameter | Type   | Description                          |
|-----------|--------|--------------------------------------|
| `q`       | string | Search query.                       |
| `limit`   | number | Specifies the number of records to return. |

### Request Body Data  
_No body data required._

---

### Example Request

```javascript
const options = {
  method: 'POST',
  url: 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/site/technology',
  params: { q: 'text', limit: '2' },
  headers: { 'User-Agent': 'insomnia/10.3.0' }
};

axios.request(options)
  .then(function (response) {
    console.log(response.data);
  })
  .catch(function (error) {
    console.error(error);
  });
```

---

