## Store Technology Data

### Endpoint  
**`POST /site/technology/store`**

---

### Request Body Data  

| Field | Type   | Validation                                      |
|-------|--------|------------------------------------------------|
| `name` | string | required                                       |
| `img`  | file   | required, image, mime types: jpeg, png, jpg, gif, svg, max size: 2048 KB |

---

### Example Request  

```javascript
const form = new FormData();
form.append("name", "abc");
form.append("img", "C:\\Users\\User\\Downloads\\Screenshot_2.png");

const options = {
  method: 'POST',
  url: 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/site/technology/store',
  headers: {
    'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data; boundary=---011000010111000001101001',
    'User-Agent': 'insomnia/10.3.0'
  },
  data: form
};

axios.request(options)
  .then(function (response) {
    console.log(response.data);
  })
  .catch(function (error) {
    console.error(error);
  });
```

---

### Example Response  

```json
{
  "status": "...",
  "message": "...",
  "data": {
    "name": "abc",
    "img": "http://127.0.0.1:8000/files/6768434312d35.png",
    "updated_at": "2024-12-22T16:50:11.000000Z",
    "created_at": "2024-12-22T16:50:11.000000Z",
    "id": 12
  }
}
```

